{"tid":2429242,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【10.31 旺角】情侶被指襲警、阻差辦公 兩人全部罪名不成立 訟費申請獲批","createTime":"2021-03-02T07:12:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T09:48:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6428a00caf7b66fc3dfcbb08c497662308da4a12","tid":2429242,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:12:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14066\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14066&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQAwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=47a1e5c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14066</a><br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第七庭<br />\n#張天雁裁判官<br />\n#1031油麻地 #裁決<br />\n<br />\n👥D2:譚 D3:郭 <br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1) [D2]襲擊在正當執行職務的警務人員<br />\n於2019年10月31日，在油麻地咸美頓街近彌敦道交界，襲擊正當執行職務的警員，即編號為21982的督察。<br />\n(2) [D3]阻礙在正當執行職務的警務人員<br />\n於同日同地，故意阻撓上述的督察。<br />\n<br />\n速報：🥳🥳兩名被告全部罪名不成立🥳🥳<br />\n✅兩名被告訟費申請獲批✅"},{"pid":"ca578e88f31059ff91cf6e3cab5deff1e766ebf3","tid":2429242,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96040b349e47de0d2b90052b93b09b71c9610c8","tid":2429242,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d22ffb84c650eba3b5c7de71dd3d31f453ad8d","tid":2429242,"uid":105905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:13:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3850148b7962dd017b60667b6e3bf81766830b7a","tid":2429242,"uid":53673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:14:04.000Z","msg":"去英國了"},{"pid":"ae496214a7c36af9e0eb2abb76097fb8fa14570f","tid":2429242,"uid":141668,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:14:48.000Z","msg":"鄭若驊同律政署食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c1cbd07a90501a9616e83364a1cc97ada91b8ce","tid":2429242,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:14:56.000Z","msg":"張天雁好似一時時<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9539030dc4b8efb5ffed5ae7cac1942712d570cf","tid":2429242,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:15:27.000Z","msg":"律政狗黑狗食撚屎"},{"pid":"d777a9b5875abeeea22ae1137516ccfd16d6e44c","tid":2429242,"uid":321059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:16:30.000Z","msg":"死黑警又諗住砌手足生豬肉<br />\n好彩手足遇到個正常官"},{"pid":"6d4254e2c56e8c0ee178f5994f2a87e28b98f808","tid":2429242,"uid":34811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6c1cbd07a90501a9616e83364a1cc97ada91b8ce","tid":2429242,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:14:56.000Z","msg":"張天雁好似一時時<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:17:12.000Z","msg":"不嬲都好正常"},{"pid":"f6e18ed77ff8ecdc53da7503ae6878c341d767fc","tid":2429242,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:17:41.000Z","msg":"審訊:<br />\n前年 10 月 31 日萬聖節，大批示威者在多區發起集會，其中一對年輕情侶在旺角被截停，任職文員的男被告被指拳打督察，其任職網媒記者的女友則被指企圖舉手分隔二人，令督察「追截慢咗一秒鐘嘅反應時間」，結果分別被控阻差辦公及襲警兩罪。案件今（ 8 日）在九龍城法院續審，男文員自辯時表示，督察在沒有任何警告下突然棍毆他，另一防暴警則毆打其女友，並揭起上衣，觸及胸部。聆訊下午繼續，屆時女記者會出庭自辯。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/10-31-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92-%E6%83%85%E4%BE%B6%E8%